---

<NavLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <div class="w-full">
    <h1 class="pb-4">Hi, I'm Matt.</h1>
    <h2 class="pb-4">I'm a Front End Developer with over 12 years experience.</h2>
    <p class="pb-4">
      I‚Äôve worked with companies both large and small, building robust, user-focused solutions across a wide range of industries. I‚Äôve made a career of diving into complex challenges‚Äîwhether that meant streamlining internal tooling for the Department of Defense, designing marketing websites for small businesses, or managing multi-domain WordPress environments with advanced custom functionality.
    </p>
    <p>
      From developing custom Retool apps to support operations at Reborn Consultants, to maintaining digital signage systems for global brands like McDonald‚Äôs and Popeyes, I bring a pragmatic approach to solving problems with clean code and thoughtful UI. At GE Aerospace, I led front-end efforts for an internal design system used by hundreds of engineers around the world, helping unify their interface standards. No matter the size of the project, I focus on delivering dependable work that bridges design and development.
